{"tid":854930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬凱事件 英外相發聲明：有政治動機","createTime":"2018-10-09T16:53:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T02:40:43.000Z","uid":176442,"like":68,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"b363d250a0a474172267fd80af73b02f5b696f58","tid":854930,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T16:53:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"169d556b4bf7db7029872976f1c403f05abaabbb","tid":854930,"uid":176442,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T16:54:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181010&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58776256\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181010%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58776256&d=5mFwTs4r%2B8edJhgIkFb5HdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=8856f7be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181010%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58776256&h=8fd00cc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181010&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58776256</a> <br />\n【封殺港獨】拒續馬凱工作簽證 英外相發聲明：有政治動機<br />\n<br />\n特區政府堅拒向任職《金融時報》的馬凱續發工作簽證一事作出解釋，事件持續升溫。英國外相侯俊偉（Jeremy Hunt）發表聲明，指非常關注今次事件，又表明在欠缺官方解釋下，只能得出事件有政治動機的結論。<br />\n<br />\n兩個月前，特區政府與中國政府先後譴責外國記者會邀請香港民族黨陳浩天發表演講，外國記者會副主席馬凱是當日的主持人。侯俊偉補充，今次事件對香港的言論和新聞自由造成破壞，兩者均受中英聯合聲明及基本法保障，事件亦為一國兩制造成壓力。<br />\n<br />\n侯俊偉促請特區政府重新考慮今次決定，指香港的權利與自由是城市邁向成功的重要基石。"},{"pid":"9a55794b42e0bd2772e947cf322250dc3b4d5204","tid":854930,"uid":21394,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T16:55:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/005456_1ab130f06df965eabed045bea6b5174a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F005456_1ab130f06df965eabed045bea6b5174a.png&h=c00a71e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國外相侯俊偉指，特區政府拒絕解釋拒續簽馬凱的工作簽證，只能得出事件有政治動機的結論。(路透社)<br />\n<br />\n特區政府堅拒向任職《金融時報》的馬凱續發工作簽證一事作出解釋，事件持續升溫。英國外相侯俊偉（Jeremy Hunt）發表聲明，指非常關注今次事件，又表明在欠缺官方解釋下，只能得出事件有政治動機的結論。<br />\n<br />\n兩個月前，特區政府與中國政府先後譴責外國記者會邀請香港民族黨陳浩天發表演講，外國記者會副主席馬凱是當日的主持人。侯俊偉補充，今次事件對香港的言論和新聞自由造成破壞，兩者均受中英聯合聲明及基本法保障，事件亦為一國兩制造成壓力。<br />\n<br />\n侯俊偉促請特區政府重新考慮今次決定，指香港的權利與自由是城市邁向成功的重要基石。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181010/58776256\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181010%2F58776256&d=5mFwTs4r%2B8edJhgIkFb5HdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=7cbe7e9e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181010%2F58776256&h=4d765ad1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181010/58776256</a>"},{"pid":"e2e6de9f32a0229264db6e1e160f5e4e696f7e25","tid":854930,"uid":13257,"like":75,"dislike":0,"score":75,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T16:56:18.000Z","msg":"英國外相<br />\n美國商會<br />\n歐盟<br />\n加拿大<br />\n<br />\n摩牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6abe13db2e1afc5ae80cd243588bbc162f195346","tid":854930,"uid":89931,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T16:56:31.000Z","msg":"又得把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有侵一成話你勁"},{"pid":"9e3851f9e203a8e75cd35802a2daa6399edec7d7","tid":854930,"uid":176442,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6abe13db2e1afc5ae80cd243588bbc162f195346","tid":854930,"uid":89931,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T16:56:31.000Z","msg":"又得把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有侵一成話你勁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T16:56:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e2a2aef44e4460523c4057e331a70d455105a8d","tid":854930,"uid":19029,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2